preference.name: MDL_export_search_results_dataset_type
preference.preference_description: Defines the type/reference of the dataset created for the MS Excel file generated by exporting the search results in the dataset_type.reference format. The default value is MSExcel.excel. If the specified dataset type/reference is invalid, the default value is used.
